  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed trial is to evaluate the use of the TORQ closure assistance device and how it
      affects pain in the sternum, breathing and quality of life compared to traditional use of
      needle drivers or similar to close sternal wires.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
